headline: Assurant and Compass International Holdings Launch New Home Warranty Solutions Across Select Brands
summary: ATLANTA, February 09, 2026--Assurant, Inc. (NYSE: AIZ), a premier global protection company that safeguards and services connected devices, homes, and automobiles in partnership with the world’s leading brands, today announced the launch of Assurant Home Warranty through a long-term relationship with six brands operating within global real estate services company Compass International Holdings ("CIH").
